snippet.title: Sanjay C
snippet.description: Music production, gear, and tips. I post videos about the latest music gear including keyboards, audio interfaces, plugins, microphones, and more. I also create music production tutorials - how to make beats, how to produce tracks, and process vocals. I compare some of the best new gear out there and always brings you the latest news happening in the music production world. Sanjay C News is a one of a kind source for the latest in music gear and plugin releases, free plugins, and the best deals. Watch my Music Gear News series every Saturday morning.
